$Id: CHANGES,v 1.2 2006/09/22 16:28:18 lafisk Exp $

COIN_2006Sep06

We had to change 3 configure scripts, so that tests
that compile code would link with libraries in the LIBS variable.
The underlying macro that needs to be changed is COIN_HAS_USER_LIBRARY,
but I couldn't run autoreconf on the directory, so I had to change
the configure scripts themselves.

I sent a message to Coin-discuss@list.coin-or.org to ask if they
could change COIN_HAS_USER_LIBRARY to use the LIBS variable with
compilations.

